    <mixer person="Alexander Hulpke" data="name_link"/>
    at Rennes, April 1996. Available in
    <a href="/Doc/Talks/rennes.tex">LaTeX</a>,
    <a href="/Doc/Talks/rennes.dvi">DVI</a>, and
    <a href="/Doc/Talks/rennes.ps">PostScript</a>.
  <br />&nbsp;
  </li>
  <li>
    An Introduction to <mixer var="GAP3"/>.<br />
    A two hour introduction for beginners by
    <mixer person="Steve Linton" data="name_link"/>,
    delivered at the workshop "Nilpotent and Soluble Quotient Methods" in
    Trento, Italy, June 1997. Available in 
    <a href="/Doc/Talks/trento.tex">LaTeX</a>,  
    <a href="/Doc/Talks/trento.dvi">DVI</a>, and
    <a href="/Doc/Talks/trento.ps">PostScript</a>.
  <br />&nbsp;
  </li>
  <li>
    An <a href="/Doc/Talks/caserta97.html">introduction to groups</a>,
    in particular finite soluble groups, in <mixer var="GAP3"/>.<br />
    Slides to talks by <mixer person="Bettina Eick" data="name_link"/>
    at the conference `Methods of computer algebra in finite geometry' in
    Caserta, Italy, November 1997.
  <br />&nbsp;
  </li>
</ul>

